{"tid":2306362,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好凍呀 凍到我縮返入被窩了","createTime":"2020-11-30T11:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T13:38:31.000Z","uid":343520,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7ce9f461bcebb11eb9c21c90d41a3f58995f01de","tid":2306362,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:23:15.000Z","msg":"好凍，頭先瞓唔着嗰陣時諗起你，發夢又諗起你，冇同你傾偈三日，每秒都有諗起你。我真係未試過咁鍾意一個人，我份人好容易放棄的，但係今次一啲放棄嘅心都冇。<br />\n<br />\n曾經有一段真摯的愛情擺喺我眼前，我冇去珍惜，等到失去左先至後悔莫及，塵世間最痛苦嘅事莫過於此，如果上天能夠比我一個重新嚟過嘅機會，我希望可以對嗰個女仔講：「我愛你」，如果一定要為呢段愛加一個期限的話，我希望係...... 一萬年。<br />\n<br />\n有啲嘢你已經講得好明顯，我都唔知點解我仲會繼續死纏爛打，可能因為我太耐冇咁鍾意過一個人。可能咁樣講好on9，但係，呢個係我而家嘅諗法，我好想比幸福你。"},{"pid":"fb026687894718a89d3796767cf8989f22ba19dc","tid":2306362,"uid":234509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89a43b34b5915d05b66284d13a1dcea02aae75d","tid":2306362,"uid":367153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:25:03.000Z","msg":"拿？"},{"pid":"53f67537adda0bb4b89b68cb73baccb4bd739d18","tid":2306362,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"咁多負評做乜"},{"pid":"598e618ee107bca9f58598c4d54faf01ae289706","tid":2306362,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d89a43b34b5915d05b66284d13a1dcea02aae75d","tid":2306362,"uid":367153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:25:03.000Z","msg":"拿？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:27:52.000Z","msg":"是一位像風一般的女子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WsEKnxc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWsEKnxc.gif&h=fe0ce89a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a372ca6450fb87a6615dfd6f21fd369cafa41a7c","tid":2306362,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fb026687894718a89d3796767cf8989f22ba19dc","tid":2306362,"uid":234509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci